summary: This is only a dungeon at the moment, I plan on turning it to a questline so stay updated on that.
descriptionHtml:
You aren\'t the only Dovahkiin in Skyrim
You recently found out another Dovahkiin is hiding in his lair
No more Questline spoilers

Adds:
+Atronachs (Dragon\'s Guards)
+New Words of Power (Dov-ah-kiin)
+New Weapons (Sadly, no custom textures, not that good yet)
+5 New Enemies (Before version 1.2 of this mod)
+1 Dragonborn
+2 Non-custom Dragons
+1 Horse mount

Adds alot
author: TriforcesofOne
